  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131780/extras/602b82594ee8df8570ee9a9cdd473066.avif?t=1716196110\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Our Hero finds himself in dangerous dungeon welcoming him with a threat – fiend who wants to steal his mustaches. To save his pride our Hero needs to pass through dangerous traps and not get fooled by “Stealer of Mustaches”.<br><br>- Do not let fiend steal your mustaches!<br>- Feel classic traps in a new way, their finesse might surprise you!<br>- Do you need to trust tips signs give you?<br>- 8-bit drive soundtrack.<br>- Magical amulet wouldn’t let you rest in peace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131780/extras/4be581accb89d03d13f2f37d0852c28a.poster.avif?t=1716196110\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131780/extras/4be581accb89d03d13f2f37d0852c28a.webm?t=1716196110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1131780/extras/4be581accb89d03d13f2f37d0852c28a.mp4?t=1716196110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
